    on log-log axes.  The power-law structure is visible as an
    approximately linear relationship.  The heavy right tail represents
    the small number of high-degree hub nodes that drive super-spreader
    dynamics.}
\end{figure}

\subsection{Epidemic Curves: Grid vs Network}

\begin{figure}[H]
