\subsection{Activity 5: Grass as a Buffer and the Extinction Optimum}
\label{sec:activity5}

\textbf{Teaching point:}  Adding a third trophic level changes not just
cycle amplitude but extinction risk, and there is an optimal grass regrowth
rate that minimises extinction probability.

\textbf{Instructions.}  Open \texttt{demo/demo\_predator\_prey.R} and
